data.description: Welcome home to 40728 La Salle Pl, nestled on a cul-de-sac in the coveted Jackson Crossing community in Murrieta with no rear neighbors and close proximity to both 15 and 215 freeways, providing an added convenience for daily commuters. This beautifully maintained 3-bedroom, 2.5 bathroom residence is the epitome of comfort and style. All bedrooms and the laundry room (washer and dryer included) are conveniently located upstairs for ease of living. The property shines with fresh exterior paint, an Alumawood back patio equipped with ceiling fans and custom lighting, new sprinklers and drip lines, a manicured grass lawn, including Apple, Lime and Lemon trees and a storage shed for your yard tools and equipment.  Enjoy the benefits of paid solar with new invertor, as well as a $5k whole house filtration & conditioning plus 6 stage alkaline drinking system (including soft water in the garage for spot-free car washes).  Experience the luxury of newer carpet and interior paint, newly updated kitchen, along with recently serviced and cleaned chimney, ducts, and wood-burning fireplace.  There is a large playground and new tamper resistant electrical outlets throughout.  Smart features include irrigation controls, thermostat and front door camera.   Residents of Jackson Crossing enjoy exclusive access to a range of amenities, including a pool, spa, playground, BBQ area, park, dog park, and RV and Boat storage.  Don't miss the opportunity to belong to this amazing community!
